dc_description_s: The Massachusetts House Legislative Districts (2002) datalayer reflects the state House of Representatives district boundaries as defined by Massachusetts General Laws, Chapter 57: Section 4. These 160 districts are those used in the Fall 2002 elections. Names of elected officials are up-to-date through January 2003. The name of the statewide datalayer is HOUSE02. This replaces the older HOUSE93 layer. - The "final" version of the 2002 House District layer.- Names of Reps fixed.- Minor edits made to name and URL spelling- Clipped to the OUTLINE coverage.
